c: 2
v: 220
t: "Kulomhlaba nakwelizayo futhi bakubuza ngezintandane ithi, “ukubasiza kungcono kepha uma nizihlanganisa nabo mayelana nesimo sabo bangabafowenu futhi uMvelinqangi uyamazi umenzi wobubi kulowo owenza okuhle, ukube uMvelinqangiubethandaubenganifakaebunzimeni.Ngempela uMvelinqangi uphakeme ngamandla unobuhlakani"